data.description: This fabulous raised ranch on a corner lot in Massillon is ready for its new owners. So many updates:  Neutral paint, white doors and trim, new carpet and luxury vinyl tile flooring, new outlets and switches, new lighting (even in the closets), new garage door, new cedar pillars and shutters.  The modern kitchen offers a light contemporary look.  The Ensuite bedroom is huge!  The lower level bedroom is very large also!  The lower level includes the family room with fireplace, the large bedroom or for any use, 1/2 bath, a large, finished utility room and a bar counter with cabinets.  Leaving the lower level, you walk out onto a spacious deck which is great for grilling or entertaining, relaxing, or bird watching.  The house has many closets for storing all your treasures.  The Lenox furnace was installed in 2019, HW Tank in 2013. You will find upwards of $50,000 in upgrades installed using licensed, professional contractors. The original builder put in an integrated heating system to efficiently heat and cool the home minimizing costs of gas and electricity. Cinch Home Warranty included.
